templates.cypher:
MATCH (a:OperationalPoint)
WHERE lower(a.name) CONTAINS lower($cityname)
RETURN a
templates.text: Show me all Operation Points in $cityname
templates.name: Show me all Operation Points in $cityname --> Malm

templates.cypher:
MATCH path=(a:OperationalPoint)-[:SECTION]->(b:OperationalPoint)
WHERE a.id STARTS WITH $countrycode
RETURN path
templates.name: Show me tracks in country eg. IT --> for Italy
